# Pitambari CMS / homepage + public QR (see USER_WEB_API.md in monorepo root).
#
# LOCAL DEV (default): Vite proxies /api → Pitambari-backend (vite.config.ts).
VITE_API_URL=/api
#
# LOCAL without proxy (either form — /api is added automatically for http(s) URLs):
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:4000
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:4000/api
#
# PRODUCTION (Vercel, Netlify, etc.): REQUIRED. Static sites have no dev proxy — set the real API:
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-pitambari-backend.example.com/api
# Also set Pitambari-backend CORS_ORIGINS to include your storefront origin (or use * for testing).

# Rewards / loyalty server vars (see README.md) — separate from CMS.
